{"tid":783894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅芯創辦人學歷做假 科大畢業扮哈佛","createTime":"2018-08-18T02:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T05:38:18.000Z","uid":5195,"like":286,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"55494a6cd481c282ab4542a92db090a4f9953ac6","tid":783894,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒《雷帝網》報道，紅芯不僅瀏覽器核心涉嫌造假，兩位創始人的履歷亦涉嫌造假。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，一篇有關創辦人陳本峰的文章介紹提到，他是科大訊飛創始成員。但科大訊飛回應指陳本峰只在公司實習過，並非創始成員。另外一位創辦人高婧在網頁介紹中，自稱畢業於美國哈佛大學及香港科技大學，但實際上她只是哈佛大學的交流學生。在紅芯瀏覽器被曝造假推上風口浪尖時，高婧網頁亦迅速更改個人履歷介紹。"},{"pid":"694e3fbe9927ff701b7196c153157fe95f3334b0","tid":783894,"uid":49258,"like":219,"dislike":0,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"大陸狗真係無樣叻, 呃人都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9384b65b4c6812eda32261ef1759c238846daf","tid":783894,"uid":8867,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9184eea6b9b8038222eeece4e661cf239238b917","tid":783894,"uid":131691,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"出貓係中囯人嘅國術嚟㗎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/102734_c087bc250d19deba12c0eb5381288146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F102734_c087bc250d19deba12c0eb5381288146.jpg&h=7ce3bebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb20488f718bb016fd5b8bdd15672f6fb1532ed9","tid":783894,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"499aad66012efbacd6a5a55f8e2ed9b1db66bafe","tid":783894,"uid":85629,"like":76,"dislike":6,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈.....佛大